{"word":"διαμοιράω","slug":"διαμοιράω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαμοιράω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to divide, rend asunder</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; so in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, also, <i>to portion out, distribute</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}